#

Easy Beef Burrito

25 min
$12
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinQuick Meal

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

MexicanComfort FoodQuickEasy

Description

A delicious and satisfying burrito filled with seasoned beef, beans, and cheese, all wrapped in a warm tortilla.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 pound
  • taco seasoning: 1 packet
  • refried beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • shredded cheese: 1 cup
  • tortillas: 4 large
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • salsa: 1/2 cup
  • lettuce: 1 cup (shredded)
